<body>

<div id="login-overlay">
  <div class="login-box">
    <h2>🎧 Staff Training Portal</h2>
    <p>Hearing Benefit Services — Internal Use Only</p>
    <input type="text" id="uname" placeholder="Username" autocomplete="username" />
    <input type="password" id="pword" placeholder="Password" autocomplete="current-password" />
    <button onclick="checkLogin()">Sign In</button>
    <p id="login-error">Incorrect username or password. Please try again.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="main-content">

  <header>
    <h1>🏷️ Contact Management — Tagging, Exporting & Importing</h1>
    <p>How to tag contacts, export lists, and import contacts between GHL accounts.</p>
  </header>

  <nav class="sticky">
    <a href="#overview">Overview</a>
    <a href="#tagging">How to Tag</a>
    <a href="#bulk-tag">Bulk Tagging</a>
    <a href="#smart-list">Smart Lists</a>
    <a href="#export">Exporting Contacts</a>
    <a href="#import">Importing Contacts</a>
    <a href="#real-example">Real Example</a>
